## Pros and Cons of Legalizing Abortion

| **Pros**                                                                 | **Cons**                                                                                   |
|--------------------------------------------------------------------------|--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| Preserves women's right to bodily autonomy and choice                    | Potential conflict between law and religious/moral beliefs                                 |
| Reduces maternal mortality and morbidity from unsafe abortions           | Possible health risks associated with abortion procedures                                  |
| Decreases unwanted pregnancies and associated socioeconomic burdens      | Ethical concerns about the moral status of the fetus                                      |
| Promotes gender equality by enabling women to control reproductive lives | Some argue it may increase divorce rates and affect societal values                       |
| Prevents unsafe, illegal abortions and their complications               | Concerns about psychological effects and potential regret                                 |
| Supports public health by allowing regulated, safe medical procedures    | Some view abortion as morally equivalent to murder                                       |

